descriptionNullable: Dataset that was webscraped from Myanimelist [webpage](https://myanimelist.net/anime/season/2022/fall) for Fall 2022 anime on November 11, 2022 and inserted into Postgresql database. The dataset was exported from said database as an Excel file, which, in addition to being uploaded here to Kaggle, was used to power a [Tableau dashboard](https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/joseph.headley/viz/FallAnime2022/Fall2022AnimeInfo) that I created.
